s="t m0 x9 h4 yf9 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">“如人饮水，冷暖自知”<span class="_ _a"></span>，不一定非要用文字来描述。 </div><div class="t m0 x5e h21 y24a ff15 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls5c ws0">（五）<span class="_ _10"></span> <span class="_ _24"> </span><span class="ff16 ls0">问<span class="ffb fs3 ls6">：<span class="_ _8"></span>我是北大哲学系的学生，<span class="_ _d"></span>想请教您：<span class="_ _15"></span><span class="ls0">《心</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y24b ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls26 ws0">经》中有“色不异空，空不异色”<span class="_ _a"></span><span class="ls22">，单从字面上看，这两句</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y24c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">话好像是一个意思，<span class="_ _7"></span>但又用不同的词语表达出来了，<span class="_ _7"></span>不知道</div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y24d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">它们在思想上、修证上是不是有很大不同？ </div><div class="t m0 x5e h3 y133 ff16 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">答<span class="ffa">：<span class="_ _23"></span><span class="fs3 ls23">“色不异空”<span class="_ _a"></span><span class="ls69">，是指色法的本体是空性。关于这一</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc1 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">点，<span class="_ _7"></span>理论上可用中观推理来抉择，<span class="_ _7"></span>窍诀上可让一个开悟者对</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc2 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">你直指。<span class="_ _8"></span>像禅宗的话，<span class="_ _8"></span>有些上师对弟子狠狠地打一打、<span class="_ _8"></span>敲一</div><div class="t m0 x9 h13 yde ff5 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">                                        <span class="_ _1d"></span>               <span class="_ _7"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h1d y16f ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3</div><div class="t m0 x65 h1e y170 ff5 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">  <span class="ff11">详见《妙法宝库<span class="_ _19"> </span></span>22<span class="ff11">—智悲清流》之《金刚经开示录》<span class="_ _26"></span>。<span class="ff5"> </span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
